export var editorProps = {
    apiKey: String,
    licenseKey: String,
    cloudChannel: String,
    id: String,
    init: Object,
    initialValue: String,
    inline: Boolean,
    modelEvents: [String, Array],
    plugins: [String, Array],
    tagName: String,
    toolbar: [String, Array],
    modelValue: String,
    disabled: Boolean,
    readonly: Boolean,
    tinymceScriptSrc: String,
    outputFormat: {
        type: String,
        validator: function (prop) { return prop === 'html' || prop === 'text'; }
    },
};
